<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
	  tal:define="lang context/i18n:user_lang"
	  tal:attributes="lang lang; xml:lang lang;" i18n:domain="ztfy.sendit">
<head>
	<title i18n:translate="">[<tal:var content="options/app/i18n:mail_subject_header" i18n:name="header" />] Download notification</title>
</head>
<body>
	<p i18n:translate="">Hello,</p>
	<p i18n:translate="">This message is a download notification from 
		<span i18n:name="service_name" tal:content="options/app/i18n:mail_service_name" /> service proposed by 
		<span i18n:name="service_owner" tal:content="options/app/i18n:mail_service_owner" />.</p>
	<p i18n:translate="">The packet <strong i18n:name="title" tal:content="options/packet/title" /> has been downloaded by <strong i18n:name="downloader" tal:content="options/downloader/title" />.</p>
	<p tal:condition="python:len(options['packet']) > 1" i18n:translate="">WARNING: you will not receive new notifications when this recipient will download other packet's document.</p>
	<p>&nbsp;</p>
	<div tal:content="structure options/app/i18n:mail_signature" />
</body>
</html>